        { question: "Which line is the better fit for the scenario?", options: ["Perfect for a fresh, glowing look.", "Best for dramatic contour only.", "Use only as an under-eye product."], correct: 0, feedback: "Correct. That line best matches the customer’s request for fresh, healthy-looking skin." },
      ],
    },
  },
  {
    id: "bronzer",
    lesson: "Lesson 5",
    title: "The Bronzer",
    visual: "bronzer",
    theme: { accent: "#d58f62", soft: "#f8f1ed", deep: "#9a633e" },
    productName: "5.1) OBC bronzer",
    overviewHeading: "5.1.1) Product Overview",
    overview: [
      "An innovative universal bronzer formula that can be used to create a radiant, sun-kissed glow to the skin, with a velvet smooth touch and natural glowing finish.",
      "Its light texture makes it bendable and buildable for a more intense sculpted finish or can be simply applied to bare skin for a natural tanned look.",
      "Contains Hoya Lacunosa Flower Extract which is rich in bioactive compounds and is known for its skin-conditioning properties. Hoya Lacunosa flower extract also helps to soothe, hydrate, and improve skin texture, while also enhancing the skin’s natural barrier and promoting a radiant and smooth complexion overall.",
      "The Bronzer contains spherical powders that allow for a homogenous and smooth application and emollient oils to maintain the physiological hydration of the skin.",
    ],
    sections: [
      { heading: "5.1.2) What it does", bullets: ["Gives the skin a radiant, sun-kissed glow", "Adds warmth and definition with a natural, glowing finish", "Applies smoothly and evenly for a soft, velvety feel", "Helps keep the skin hydrated and comfortable"] },
      { heading: "5.1.3) How to use it", subsections: [{ label: "Light application:", bullets: ["Apply to bare skin for a natural, tanned look"] }, { label: "Buildable application:", bullets: ["Build it up for a more sculpted, defined finish"] }] },
      { heading: "5.1.4) Who is it for", label: "Customers who:", bullets: ["Want a healthy, sun-kissed look.", "Like a natural glow or a more sculpted finish.", "Want bronzer that blends easily.", "Want make-up that still feels good on the skin."] },
      { heading: "5.1.5) How to sell", bullets: ["“This gives your skin a natural, sun-kissed glow.”", "“You can keep it soft and natural or build it for more definition.”", "“It blends easily and doesn’t look patchy or heavy.”"] },
      { heading: "5.1.6) When to Recommend", paragraph: "Recommend this when a customer wants warmth, glow, or light contouring without harsh lines." },
